# Expectancy Value Theory

Focues on a lerners expectancy and subjective task value

Expectancy is a learners belif about where they can produce a successful outcome for a task

Task avlue is a learner's subjective assesment of the value of a succes or faloue of a task

Task value ahs 4 components
>importance (to self, identiy, or community)
>intrinisic value
>utility value
>cost

